originalText.text: Using Central Park Pedicab for my visit to Central Park was an absolute delight! The friendly and knowledgeable pedicab drivers made the whole experience enjoyable and relaxing. I was able to sit back and take in the breathtaking views of the park while learning interesting facts about its history and landmarks. The pedicabs were comfortable and well-maintained, allowing me to fully enjoy the beauty of Central Park without any hassle. It was a fantastic way to explore the park at a leisurely pace, stopping at picturesque spots for photos and taking in the fresh air. I highly recommend Central Park Pedicab for anyone looking for a unique and memorable way to experience the iconic Central Park.

originalText.text:
I’ ve lived in New York for 10 years and never taken a pedicab before, but let me tell I m glad I finally did.  I booked a pedicab tour with MYNY TOUR, when my family was visiting the Big Apple in June.
These guys are true pros in their business. The picked us up from our hotel in TSQ and gave an 1 hour tour in Central Park. They showed all the highlights of the park, told us the history, after that we’re dropped off at our restaurant where we had our reservation. It was hassle free, smooth operation. I really enjoyed it and without a doubt, hands down, would recommend them to anyone. 100% satisfaction guaranteed. I stamp my seal of approval for these guys.
